name: Dacpac-data-migrations
tagline: Deploy your database without data lose with dacpac
body:
If you wander is it possible to deploy your MS Sql Server database automatically without data loss...

The answer is **YES** this project will help you.

[nuget](https://www.nuget.org/packages/DacpacDataMigrations/)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
